snippet.title: HalfMoon Adventures Teaser | 2Bit Couch Games
snippet.description:
HalfMoon Adventures Teaser Trailer

https://store.steampowered.com/app/3192210/HalfMoon_Adventures/

You own a store for weekend adventurers and sell maps of dungeons.
You sell maps during the day and crawl through dungeons at night. 
However - the market for map sellers is in high demand.Try to offer the best maps and push your competitor out of the market! 

Wishlist on Steam!
More updates will follow.
